-- MoneyGram slashes 2014 forecast as Wal-Mart looms
-- By Tanya Agrawal in Bangalore
-- Tue Apr 29, 2014 08:03AM EDT
-- None



April 29 (Reuters) - MoneyGram International Inc <MGI.O>, the world's second-largest money transfer company, slashed its forecast for 2014 on fears of competition from Wal-Mart Stores Inc <WMT.N>.

Wal-Mart said this month that it will launch a money transfer service called "Walmart-2-Walmart". [ID:nL2N0N90RN]